，你那自以为是的聪明和藐视一切的优越感迟早要毁了你。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IyMiE8abRhoY5EAMaCDY5NzAxMTk4IIbNrokGMAA4yAFAKnIJNDgzMzg3MjU2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-ee31efb1f00403d8ffbeec5ed1ba8f82_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"43_1633911881.4881794","card_id":"Q_23349029","target":{"id":23349029,"title":"为什么有些男生喜欢搞暧昧？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/23349029","type":"question","created":1397051557,"answer_count":359,"follower_count":2293,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[307,4728,10486,14159,83626],"comment_count":25,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"忽冷忽热，若即若离，一会暧昧，一会又不理。"},"attached_info":"Cj0IyMiE8abRhoY5EAMaBzE1MjA5MzkgpaGVmgUwGTj1EUArcggyMzM0OTAyOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-932e9976ceb88d5554e5c518ea17ef3b_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"44_1633911881.4884853","card_id":"Q_483461416","target":{"id":483461416,"title":"2021 届毕业生现在都过得怎么样？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/483461416","type":"question","created":1630292623,"answer_count":461,"follower_count":1274,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2029,2611,11758,14421,726204],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"希望大家一起分享自己的生活。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IyMiE8abRhoY5EAMaCDY5NzE3NzU4II+VsYkGMAA4+glALHIJNDgzNDYxNDE2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"45_1633911881.4887614","card_id":"Q_41429192","target":{"id":41429192,"title":"罗森、7-11